Policy.acknowledgement_statement: Samples and associated genotype and phenotype data used in this study were provided by Vanderbilt University Medical Center. Funding support was provided by the National Heart, Lung, and Blood Institute (NHLBI) grants R01-HL079184 and U01-HL065962, and the RIKEN Institute.
Policy.ic_specific_access_term: Use of this data is limited to health/medical/biomedical purposes, does not include the study of population origins or ancestry. The informed consent document signed by the “Pharmacogenetics of ACE Inhibitor-Associated Angioedema” study participants allows use of these data by investigators employed by non-profit and for-profit organizations. These data may be used by only for genetic studies to learn about, prevent, or treat health problems. This consent group does not require IRB approval.
